'''Friedrich Wilhelm Nietzsche''' d afelsafi analman, yella d aɣen d amedyaz, d afilulug. Ilul ass n 15 tuber 1844 di Röcken, yemmut di  Prusya ass n 25 ɣuct 1900 (tamurt n Lalman).
Yettneḥsab seg ifelsafiyen imeqqranen i qqaren madden s tudget ar assa ; imahilen-is bnan s umata ɣef usenqed n yidles aɣerbi atrar d wayen akk i yejmel d azalen n lmeεna i d-yekkan seg ufesser n wesɣan amasiḥi, i yettnadi ad ibeddel s wiyaḍ i d-yewwi d imaynuten, am akken i d-iwet deg tanga d wassɣ-is d umdan. Si tama nniḍen yura daɣen ɣef trumanṣit tanalmant, acku yella yelha-d d tesnilest d wayen akk yerzan tutlayin d warraten iqburen.
